<h2>Sign Up</h2>

<p style="color: red; display: none">NOTE: We have reached our quota for
membership in the Stadium Chorus for 2011.  You may, however, sign up here in
order to be contacted for participation in future years.  Thank you for your
interest.</p>

<% if flash[:error] %>
  <div id="error-message"><%= flash[:error] %></div>
<% end %>

<form action="/do_signup" method="post">
  <table id="signup-form">
    <%= @form.as_table %>
  </table>

  <font color="red"><em>Please click this button <b>only once</b>
  (it might take a minute):</em></font><br>
  <input type="submit" value="Add Me" /> <strong>to the contact list</strong>

  <br><br>
  <p class="notice">NOTE: If anthing goes wrong with the form submission, please
  email stadium<foo>choir<foo>@<foo>twoedge<foo>.<foo>com with a precise
  description of what happened.</p>
</form>
